---
title: Turkey and Orzo Stew with Feta and Tortilla Crumble
description: Mexican seasoning adds bold flavour to this hearty stew.  Ground turkey joins sweet peppers and fresh spinach in an aromatic tomato broth, before being topped with a spiced tortilla chip crumble and feta cheese.
